videos.headline: Johnson grabs back-shoulder throw for TD
videos.description: QB Tanner Morgan fires a ball into the end zone for Tyler Johnson who makes the grab to put Minnesota ahead 10-0 on Georgia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Johnson grabs back-shoulder throw for TD) 2018/12/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: 41-yard sideline catch sets up Minnesota TD
videos.description: Chris Autman-Bell steps out of bounds after a 41-yard reception near the sideline, then Mohamed Ibrahim runs it in on the next play to put Minnesota up 20-3.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech punches in 1st TD
videos.description: Nathan Cottrell breaks free for a 20-yard touchdown, narrowing Georgia Tech's deficit to 20-10.

videos.headline: Ibrahim runs in his 2nd TD of game
videos.description: Mohamed Ibrahim puts Minnesota up big with his second touchdown of the game, giving the Golden Gophers a 27-10 advantage.

videos.headline: Ibrahim surpasses 200 yards in game
videos.description: Mohamed Ibrahim becomes the first Minnesota player since 2014 to eclipse 200 rushing yards on a 33-yard run down the sideline.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech QB fumbles in final minute to ice Quick Lane Bowl
videos.description: QB Tobias Oliver fumbles with under a minute remaining to secure Minnesota's victory over Georgia Tech in the 2018 Quick Lane Bowl.
